app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2223-7747/10/1/70/s1, Time laps photo-documentation of somatic embryogenesis from Centaurium erythraea leaf culture is provided in a form of a video file Centaury somatic embryogenesis.mp4. The size of the video is about 25 Mb.
